edu.cmu.sei.arche.rfconfig
Class ConfigReader

java.lang.Object
  edu.cmu.sei.arche.rfconfig.ConfigReader
public class ConfigReader
extends java.lang.Object

ConfigReader class is responsible for parsing an RF configuration file, creating an instance of ReasoningFrameworkVO class and populating it with data from the configuration file

Author:
Alexander Berendeyev
